article_text:
Double Take 'Toons: Obamacare All Fired Up?

Many claim that the coming implementation of key parts of the Affordable Care Act will hurt working Americans. Joel Pett thinks that's not honest criticism, while John Deering looks at the delays and waivers and wonders what's left.

toggle caption Joel Pett
